OL,9,FItaly is in the midst of its third
OL,10,Fheatwave of the summer, with tourists
OL,11,Fin 16 cities advised to stay indoors
OL,12,Fduring the day as temperatures this
OL,13,Fweek near 40C.
OL,15,FAs "Nero", an anticyclone of hot air
OL,16,Ffrom the Saharan desert, brings
OL,17,Fsignificantly hotter weather to the
OL,18,Fcountry's central and northern
OL,19,Fregions, the whole Alpine region is
OL,20,Ffeeling the impact.
